body:
To customize how MongoDB Search breaks text into tokens, you can
define a [Custom analyzers](custom-analyzers) in the
`analyzers` field of your MongoDB Search index.

```json
{
  "analyzers": [
    {
      "name": "<custom-analyzer-name>",
      "tokenizer": {
        "type": "<tokenizer-type>"
      }
    },
    ...
  ]
}
```
